{"tid":827702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰航機印錯字　「CATHAY PACIIC」淪國際笑話","createTime":"2018-09-19T06:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T12:39:58.000Z","uid":165282,"like":107,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"0cc085c7540ea4b3d532d440af9241f9d8d84af8","tid":827702,"uid":165282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/photo/bkn-20180919110920975-0919_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180919131930\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180919%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180919110920975-0919_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180919131930&h=6f0fa5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">國泰航空航機外的PACIFIC字樣印漏「F」字。(互聯網)</span><br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名節節下跌的國泰航空，其航機竟出現串錯品牌名字的國際笑話。互聯網流傳數張國泰航機的照片，相中停在地面的國泰航機，機身上原印國泰英文名「CATHAY PACIFIC」，變成錯印「CATHAY PACIIC」， 「PACIIC」漏了個「F」字。 <br />\n<br />\n照片所見，航機機身白色，當員工發現品牌印錯字後，一名員工在升降台上將「PACIIC」後的「IC」2個字母遮蓋，相信再重新整理才可出廠。 <br />\n<br />\n東網正向國泰查詢事件，國泰航空在其Facebook專頁亦借網圖並貼文回應：【 突發！期間限定 777 機隊外觀 】特別版向來一瞬即逝。因此她正返回基地重新塗裝。再見！ <br />\n<br />\n《國泰航空，愈做愈燶》專頁：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/fea/cx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ffea%2Fcx%2F&d=vWTFKYeVB2iqjjbcuzELvEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5df828ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/fea/cx/</a> <br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/mobile/bkn-20180919110920975-0919_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180919%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180919110920975-0919_00822_001.html&d=vWTFKYeVB2iqjjbcuzELvEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=daf2f91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180919/mobile/bkn-20180919110920975-0919_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9cce131f82e0feec59d1a8d2f0399739b5cabc16","tid":827702,"uid":191812,"like":250,"dislike":2,"score":248,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19